We were given instructions while finding out make a film of world headquarters and what

00:01:22.780 --> 00:01:25.900
we do here and show it in film.

00:01:25.900 --> 00:01:32.060
Well, I thought it was a great idea myself because I was interested in photography.

00:01:32.060 --> 00:01:34.379
Bethel means the house of God.

00:01:34.379 --> 00:01:39.900
How many people would like to visit here and don't have the opportunity and let them see

00:01:39.900 --> 00:01:46.700
what the new world society is in action because I think a tour through this place will give

00:01:46.700 --> 00:01:50.459
them the concept of the whole organization.

